Depends:        python3-nqrustbackup, nqrustbackup-filedaemon
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - contributed tools
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides some additional tools, not part of the NQRustBackup project.
